<h2>About Me</h2>
<div class="profile-img">[Image Placeholder]</div> <!-- Placeholder for your profile image -->
<p>I'm Steph Minaya, a polyglot who speaks English, Spanish, and Italian. My passion for learning and growing has been shaped by my ADHD, dyslexia, and autism. This journey has given me unique tools, like transforming vibrant bird colors into language, allowing me to express myself in ways I never thought possible.</p>

 <p>I've faced challenges but overcame them through resilience, creativity, and mentorship. I'd love to share my story and connect with your community to inspire neurodiverse students to thrive.</p>
